Field definitions:
- known_threats: list of identified threat actors, attack vectors, and threat scenarios relevant to this product and risk domain
- existing_controls: list of security controls, policies, and safeguards currently in place (include control type and maturity level)
- compliance_gaps: list of specific compliance requirements not yet met, with the applicable framework cited
- incident_patterns: list of recurring incident types, root causes, or systemic weaknesses surfaced from incident reports
- vendor_risks: list of third-party and supply chain risks identified from vendor agreements, assessments, or known exposure
- open_questions: list of questions that must be answered before a complete risk assessment can be produced

Be exhaustive — omissions here will propagate to all downstream artifacts. Return only valid JSON, no prose outside the JSON object.
